OL,7,FMany of the whistleblowers we have
OL,8,Fspoken up to describe how they have
OL,9,Fraised their concerns, but they are
OL,10,Fnot taken seriously.
OL,12,FOne staff member told us: "You expect
OL,13,Ffor them to get dealt with, and you're
OL,14,Fpromised it will get but it never
OL,15,Fdoes. Often the perpetrators get
OL,16,Fpromoted higher and higher so they are
OL,17,Faway from the person reporting the
OL,18,Fproblem in the first place".
