OL,7,FThe Welsh Government minister who
OL,8,Foversees fire services has resisted
OL,9,Fcalls for Wales-wide review, despite
OL,10,Fmounting pressure from opposition
OL,11,Fparties.
OL,13,FFirst Minister has also downplayed
OL,14,Fcalls, saying there "was always going
OL,15,Fto be some rough weather along the
OL,16,Fway".
