OL,7,FHowever, whistleblowers we have spoken
OL,8,Fto think such action is vital. One
OL,9,Fcurrent staff member said: "We would
OL,10,Fbe queuing up to speak out if the
OL,11,Fmeans to do so were safe and supported
OL,12,Fvia a cultural review".
OL,14,FAnother said they could not believe a
OL,15,Freview was being resisted. They said:
OL,16,F"If we've nothing to hide, why are we
OL,17,Fnot having an all-Wales cultural
OL,18,Freview? I don't understand it."
